So you're a pet?

1023
00:56:29,340 --> 00:56:30,650
大概是吧
I suppose.

1024
00:56:32,180 --> 00:56:34,140
人们一般都养可爱的宠物
People usually want cute pets.

1025
00:56:34,670 --> 00:56:36,740
伊戈怎么会养个这么面目可憎的
Why would Ego want such a hideous one?

1026
00:56:37,210 --> 00:56:38,490
我面目可憎吗
I am hideous?

1027
00:56:38,490 --> 00:56:41,220
你简直丑得惊心动魄
You are horrifying to look at. Yes.

1028
00:56:43,900 --> 00:56:45,340
但那是好事
But that's a good thing.

1029
00:56:46,580 --> 00:56:48,200
如果你长得丑  还有人爱你
When you're ugly, and someone loves you

1030
00:56:48,200 --> 00:56:50,140
你知道那人是爱你这个人
you know they love you for who you are.

1031
00:56:52,200 --> 00:56:54,600
美丽的人永远不知道谁能信任
Beautiful people never know who to trust.

1032
00:56:54,600 --> 00:56:57,900
那我庆幸我很丑
Well, then I'm certainly grateful to be ugly.

1033
00:56:59,870 --> 00:57:03,090
那些池塘  让我想起了有次
Those pools, they remind me of a time...

1034
00:57:03,090 --> 00:57:06,540
我带女儿去我母星的遗忘湖
when I took my daughter to the forgotten lakes of my homeworld.

1035
00:57:08,030 --> 00:57:09,400
她跟你很像
She was like you.

1036
00:57:09,700 --> 00:57:10,910
难看吗
Disgusting?

1037
