What are you talking about?

1045
00:58:09,560 --> 00:58:10,570
螳螂
Mantis...

1046
00:58:10,810 --> 00:58:12,830
你能带我们去我们的住处吗
can you show us where we'll be staying?

1047
00:58:14,020 --> 00:58:15,850
这颗星球上怎么没有其他生物
Why are there no other beings on this planet?

1048
00:58:15,850 --> 00:58:17,970
这星球就是伊戈
The planet is Ego.

1049
00:58:18,170 --> 00:58:21,100
狗不会邀请跳蚤来他背上住
A dog would not invite a flea to live on his back.

1050
00:58:21,220 --> 00:58:22,570
你不是跳蚤
And you're not a flea?

1051
