Nothing.

1055
00:58:38,470 --> 00:58:40,240
你们的住处在这边
Your quarters are this way.

1056
00:58:48,100 --> 00:58:50,620
我们明早把你们送去给克里人
We deliver you to the Kree in the morning.

1057
00:58:53,790 --> 00:58:56,760
之后你俩都活不长了
Neither one of you will last much longer after that.

1058
00:58:57,710 --> 00:58:59,380
好啊  电击脸
Okay, Taserface.

1059
00:59:00,670 --> 00:59:04,220
替我们跟其他人问好  电击脸
Tell the other guys we said "Hi," Taserface!

1060
00:59:09,550 --> 00:59:11,910
这颗小植物呢  要我用石头砸碎它吗
What about this little plant? Can I smash it with a rock?

1061
00:59:11,910 --> 00:59:13,400
不行  杰夫
No, Gef.

1062
00:59:13,400 --> 00:59:15,110
这么可爱怎么能杀掉
It's too adorable to kill.

1063
00:59:15,490 --> 00:59:16,880
送去裁缝那里
Take it to the tailor.

1064
00:59:18,760 --> 00:59:21,840
别介意  但你的雇员都是混蛋
No offense, but your employees are a bunch of jerks.

1065
00:59:24,600 --> 00:59:29,510
我做了20年的克里人战奴  是斯塔卡解救了我
I was a Kree battle slave for 20 years when Stakar freed me.

1066
00:59:31,380 --> 00:59:33,990
他邀我加入了掠夺者
He offered me a place with the Ravagers.

1067
00:59:34,700 --> 00:59:38,220
