He said all I needed to do was adhere to the code.

1068
00:59:39,390 --> 00:59:40,820
但我年轻
But I was young...

1069
00:59:42,170 --> 00:59:45,440
贪心  愚蠢
and greedy, and stupid.

1070
00:59:46,430 --> 00:59:48,590
就像你  偷了那些电池
Like you stealing those batteries.

1071
00:59:48,590 --> 00:59:50,260
那更多是德拉克斯干的
That was mostly Drax.

1072
00:59:51,870 --> 00:59:54,730
我和斯塔卡  还有其他船长
Me and Stakar and the other captains...

1073
00:59:56,270 --> 00:59:58,680
我们跟你和你的朋友很像
we weren't so different from you and your friends.

1074
00:59:59,620 --> 01:00:01,600
那是我唯一的家庭
The only family I ever had.

1075
