我活该如此
This is what I deserve.

1078
01:00:11,380 --> 01:00:13,390
等等  矫情女王
Slow down, drama queen.

1079
01:00:13,390 --> 01:00:14,950
你或许是活该  但我不是
You might deserve this, but I don't.

1080
01:00:14,950 --> 01:00:16,350
我们得逃出去
We gotta get outta here.

1081
01:00:18,390 --> 01:00:19,490
奎尔呢
Where's Quill?

1082
01:00:20,370 --> 01:00:22,000
他跟他老爸走了
He went off with his old man.

1083
01:00:22,970 --> 01:00:24,580
-伊戈  -对
- Ego? - Yeah.

1084
01:00:24,940 --> 01:00:26,750
今天净是些蠢蛋名字
It's a day for dumbass names.

1085
