我需要你去找样东西  然后拿来给我
There's something I need you to get, and bring back to me.

1104
01:02:06,080 --> 01:02:10,320
在船长室  有个原型机机械鳍
In the captain's quarters, there's a prototype fin...

1105
01:02:10,570 --> 01:02:12,360
就是我脑袋上戴的那玩意
the thing I wore on my head.

1106
01:02:12,570 --> 01:02:16,850
床铺旁边有个抽屉  就在里面  红色的
There's a drawer next to the bunk. It's in that. It's red.

1107
01:02:16,850 --> 01:02:17,850
懂了吗
You got it?

1108
