那是我的内裤
That's my underwears.

1109
01:02:53,570 --> 01:02:54,340
嗯  我就觉得
Yeah, I was pretty sure

1110
01:02:54,340 --> 01:02:55,780
他根本就没听懂你说什么
he didn't know what you were talkin' about.

1111
