You have to explain it more careful.

1112
01:02:59,400 --> 01:03:02,890
是个原型机机械鳍
It's a prototype fin.

1113
01:03:08,180 --> 01:03:11,160
那是只奥罗尼  机械鳍  格鲁特
That's an orloni. It's a fin, Groot.

1114
01:03:11,160 --> 01:03:12,910
