会不知道
and he's not gonna know

1123
01:03:28,960 --> 01:03:31,020
他的眼睛去哪了
where his eye is!

1124
01:03:37,600 --> 01:03:39,000
那是张桌子
That's a desk.

1125
01:03:39,390 --> 01:03:41,420
我们说了那玩意才这么大
We told you it was this big.

1126
01:03:48,060 --> 01:03:50,200
拜托告诉我你们船上有个冰箱
Tell me you guys have a refrigerator somewhere

1127
01:03:50,200 --> 01:03:52,360
里面全是切下来的人脚趾
with a bunch of severed human toes.

1128
