That's not what I said!

1134
01:04:18,570 --> 01:04:20,750
-我是格鲁特  -他很庆幸你不要求他那么做
- I am Groot. - He's relieved you don't want him to.

1135
01:04:20,750 --> 01:04:22,550
-我是格鲁特  -他讨厌帽子
- I am Groot. - He hates hats.

1136
01:04:22,550 --> 01:04:23,340
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1137
01:04:23,340 --> 01:04:24,750
讨厌任何人戴帽子  不仅是他自己
On anyone, not just himself.

1138
01:04:24,750 --> 01:04:25,490
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1139
01:04:25,490 --> 01:04:27,310
你还以为谁的脑袋形状很怪
One minute you think someone has a weird-shaped head

1140
01:04:27,310 --> 01:04:28,310
结果转眼发现
the next minute it's just because

1141
01:04:28,310 --> 01:04:30,230
原来那脑袋上戴了顶帽子
you realize part of that head is the hat.

1142
01:04:30,610 --> 01:04:32,130
所以你才不喜欢帽子
That's why you don't like hats?

1143
01:04:32,750 --> 01:04:35,290
