你会炸掉整艘船的
The whole ship's gonna blow.

1156
01:09:39,200 --> 01:09:40,720
不会是整艘船
Not the whole ship.

1157
01:09:57,880 --> 01:09:58,730
你是谁
Who is this?

1158
01:09:58,730 --> 01:10:02,900
我要把勇度的飞船的坐标发你
I am sending you the coordinates for Yondu's ship.

1159
01:10:03,760 --> 01:10:05,590
-释放飞行舱  -是  船长
- Release the quadrant! - Aye, Captain!

1160
01:10:05,590 --> 01:10:08,050
我只求一件事
I only ask one thing.

1161
01:10:08,660 --> 01:10:10,540
你们的大祭司
That your High Priestess

1162
01:10:10,540 --> 01:10:14,310
要告诉他是谁注定了他的毁灭
tell him the name of the man what sealed his fate.

1163
01:10:15,020 --> 01:10:16,970
电击脸
Taserface!

1164
01:10:40,570 --> 01:10:41,750
去哪  船长
Where to, Captain?

1165
01:10:41,760 --> 01:10:42,800
伊戈
Ego.

1166
01:10:44,440 --> 01:10:45,920
不行
No, boy!

1167
01:10:53,160 --> 01:10:55,420
对于哺乳类来说
It ain't healthy for a mammalian body

1168
01:10:55,420 --> 01:10:58,120
一下跳跃50次以上对身体有害
to hop more than 50 jumps at a time.

1169
01:10:58,120 --> 01:10:59,320
我知道
I know that.

1170
01:10:59,330 --> 01:11:02,070
我们要跳700次了
We are about to do 700!

1171
01:11:15,490 --> 01:11:17,970
那么这一切有一天都可能属于我喽
So I guess this could all be mine someday.

1172
01:11:18,980 --> 01:11:21,820
火箭  火箭  你在吗
Rocket? Rocket, are you there?

1173
01:11:28,740 --> 01:11:30,080
你在干什么  彼得
What are you doing, Peter?

1174
01:11:32,860 --> 01:11:33,970
跟我跳舞吧
Dance with me.

1175
01:11:34,480 --> 01:11:35,890
我才不跟你跳舞
I'm not going to dance with you.

1176
01:11:35,890 --> 01:11:37,720
这是山姆·库克的歌
This is Sam Cooke

1177
01:11:38,190 --> 01:11:40,840
