01:25:13,020 --> 01:25:16,730
也会提醒你  你内心的空虚多大多深
reminds you how big and empty that hole inside you actually is.

1360
01:25:16,730 --> 01:25:17,670
我叫你闭嘴了
I said shut up!

1361
01:25:17,670 --> 01:25:19,650
我知道那些制造了你的科学家
I know them scientists what made you,

1362
01:25:19,650 --> 01:25:21,660
根本没在乎过你
never gave a rat's ass about you.

1363
01:25:21,660 --> 01:25:22,520
我说真的  哥们
I'm serious, dude!

1364
01:25:22,520 --> 01:25:25,980
就像我自己的父母  他们把我
Just like my own damn parents who sold me

1365
01:25:25,980 --> 01:25:28,430
他们的亲生儿子  卖去做奴隶
their own little baby, into slavery.

1366
01:25:28,490 --> 01:25:30,960
我知道你是什么人  小子
I know who you are, boy.

1367
01:25:30,960 --> 01:25:32,860
因为你是我
Because you're me.

1368
01:25:39,440 --> 01:25:41,530
我们是一对儿什么样的人啊
What kind of a pair are we?

1369
01:25:42,860 --> 01:25:45,870
大概是一对儿要去对付一颗星球的人吧
The kind that's about to go fight a planet, I reckon.

1370
01:25:46,050 --> 01:25:48,470
好啊  好嘞  很好
All right, okay! Good.

1371
01:25:48,520 --> 01:25:49,540
等等
Wait.

1372
01:25:49,580 --> 01:25:50,780
对付什么
Fight a what?

1373
01:25:55,020 --> 01:25:56,380
你们是什么人
Who are you people?

1374
01:25:56,380 --> 01:25:57,130
这地方是什么
What is this place?

1375
01:25:57,130 --> 01:25:58,700
卡魔拉  放了她
Gamora, let her go!

1376
01:25:58,830 --> 01:26:01,260
洞里的尸体  他们是谁
The bodies in the caverns... Who are they?

1377
01:26:01,390 --> 01:26:03,340
你在害怕
You are scared.

1378
01:26:06,480 --> 01:26:09,740
我称之为扩张
I call it the Expansion.

1379
01:26:10,840 --> 01:26:12,480
这是我的目标
It is my purpose

1380
01:26:12,680 --> 01:26:13,600
现在
and now

1381
01:26:14,300 --> 01:26:17,790
它也是你的目标了
it is yours as well.

1382
01:26:18,780 --> 01:26:20,160
好美啊
It's beautiful.

1383
01:26:21,480 --> 01:26:23,560
数千年来
Over thousands of years,

1384
01:26:23,560 --> 01:26:27,200
我将数千个我的延伸根植在了
I implanted thousands of extensions of myself

1385
01:26:27,200 --> 01:26:29,730
数千个世界上
on thousands of worlds.

1386
01:26:30,010 --> 01:26:33,980
我得实现生命唯一真正的目标
I need to fulfill life's one true purpose...

1387
01:26:34,030 --> 01:26:36,140
生长  传播
To grow and spread

1388
01:26:36,150 --> 01:26:39,360
覆盖一切存在
covering all that exists

1389
01:26:39,360 --> 01:26:43,630
直到一切都
until everything is...

1390
01:26:44,930 --> 01:26:45,780
变成我
Me!

1391
01:26:46,490 --> 01:26:48,040
她对我做了什么
What did she do to me?

1392
01:26:48,890 --> 01:26:50,610
她已经把一切都告诉我了
She already told me everything.

1393
01:26:50,620 --> 01:26:53,170
我只有一个问题
I only had one problem.

1394
01:26:53,990 --> 01:26:55,640
一个天神
A single Celestial

1395
01:26:55,640 --> 01:26:58,470
是没有足够能量完成这样的伟业的
doesn't have enough power for such an enterprise.

1396
01:26:59,470 --> 01:27:01,450
但两个天神
But two Celestials...

1397
01:27:01,450 --> 01:27:04,840
那或许就可以了
Well, now, that just might do.

1398
01:27:07,580 --> 01:27:08,850
那些尸体
The bodies...

1399
01:27:09,740 --> 01:27:11,170
都是他的孩子
are his children.

1400
01:27:12,600 --> 01:27:14,330
我所做的一切中
Out of all my labors

1401
01:27:14,330 --> 01:27:15,450
我最喜欢的
the most beguiling

1402
01:27:15,450 --> 01:27:19,750
就是尝试将我的DNA嫁接到其他物种上
was attempting to graft my DNA with that of another species.

1403
01:27:19,850 --> 01:27:22,330
我原本希望这样的配对
I hoped the result of such a coupling

1404
01:27:22,330 --> 01:27:24,910
足以为扩张提供能量
would be enough to power the Expansion.

1405
01:27:25,850 --> 01:27:28,610
我让勇度把一些后代送来给我
I had Yondu deliver some of them to me.

1406
01:27:28,610 --> 01:27:30,240
这有违掠夺者的准则
It broke the Ravager code,

1407
01:27:30,240 --> 01:27:33,500
但我慷慨地赔偿了他
but I compensated him generously and

1408
01:27:33,500 --> 01:27:36,030
而且为安抚他的良心  我说我绝不会伤害他们
to ease his conscience, I said I'd never hurt them.

1409
01:27:36,060 --> 01:27:38,710
这倒不假  他们都毫无感觉
I mean, that was true. They never felt a thing.

1410
01:27:38,780 --> 01:27:41,660
但他们一个个都让我失望了
But one after the other, they failed me.

1411
01:27:42,310 --> 01:27:45,460
没有一个携带了天神基因
Not one of them carried the Celestial genes.

1412
01:27:46,100 --> 01:27:47,490
直到你  彼得
Until you, Peter.

1413
01:27:48,720 --> 01:27:50,840
我所有的后裔里
Out of all my spawn,

1414
01:27:51,430 --> 01:27:55,610
只有你继承了与光的联系
only you carried the connection to the light.

1415
01:27:55,810 --> 01:27:58,700
我们得马上找到彼得  离开这个破星球
We need to find Peter now, and get off this damn planet.

1416
01:27:58,700 --> 01:28:01,380
伊戈现在肯定已经拉拢了他
Ego will have won him to his side by now.

1417
01:28:01,380 --> 01:28:03,080
-他有办法...  -那我们直接走吧
- He has a way of... - Then we just go.

1418
01:28:03,080 --> 01:28:04,060
不行
No!

1419
01:28:04,190 --> 01:28:05,180
他是我们的朋友
He's our friend.

1420
01:28:05,190 --> 01:28:07,620
你们就成天冲彼此大吼
All any of you do is yell at each other.

1421
01:28:07,620 --> 01:28:08,800
你们才不是朋友
You are not friends.

1422
01:28:08,800 --> 01:28:09,870
你是对的
You're right.

1423
01:28:11,040 --> 01:28:12,120
我们是家人
We're family.

1424
01:28:13,760 --> 01:28:15,210
我们不丢下任何人
We leave no one behind.

1425
01:28:18,780 --> 01:28:19,940
或许除了你
Except maybe you.

1426
01:28:20,690 --> 01:28:22,120
天呐
Oh, my God.

1427
01:28:22,120 --> 01:28:24,600
我存在以来首次
For the first time in my existence,

1428
01:28:25,130 --> 01:28:27,960
真正不再孤单了
I am truly not alone!

1429
01:28:33,520 --> 01:28:34,750
怎么了  儿子
What is it, son?

1430
01:28:38,090 --> 01:28:39,330
我的朋友们
My friends.

1431
01:28:40,430 --> 01:28:44,680
你瞧  这就是你人性的一面  彼得
You see, that's the mortal in you, Peter.

1432
01:28:45,450 --> 01:28:46,170
是啊
Yes.

1433
01:28:46,170 --> 01:28:49,060
我们超越了那些东西
We are beyond such things.

1434
01:28:49,060 --> 01:28:50,090
是啊
Yes.

1435
01:28:52,810 --> 01:28:54,340
-好了  -但我母亲
- Now... - But my mother...

1436
01:28:57,040 --> 01:28:59,120
你说你爱我母亲的
You said you loved my mother.

1437
01:28:59,400 --> 01:29:00,870
我是爱她
And that I did.

1438
01:29:02,120 --> 01:29:03,740
我的水百合
My river lily who knew

1439
01:29:03,740 --> 01:29:07,140
她会唱收音机里播放的每一首歌
all the words to every song that came over the radio.

1440
01:29:08,880 --> 01:29:11,570
我三次回到地球看她
I returned to Earth to see her three times.

1441
01:29:11,570 --> 01:29:13,950
我知道  如果我再第四次回去
And I knew if I returned a fourth...

1442
01:29:14,450 --> 01:29:15,750
我就再不会走了
I'd never leave.

1443
01:29:17,110 --> 01:29:18,260
扩张
The Expansion...

1444
01:29:20,210 --> 01:29:22,480
我存在的目的  就完了
the reason for my very existence, would be over.

1445
01:29:22,480 --> 01:29:24,050
所以我做了我必须做的
So, I did what I had to do.

1446
01:29:24,940 --> 01:29:25,960
但是
But

1447
01:29:27,420 --> 01:29:30,620
让她患上脑瘤简直伤透了我的心
it broke my heart to put that tumor in her head.

1448
01:29:35,450 --> 01:29:36,260
什么
What?

1449
01:29:36,260 --> 01:29:37,330
好吧
Now, all right...

1450
01:29:37,330 --> 01:29:40,380
我知道这听上去很不好
I know that sounds bad.

1451
01:29:50,310 --> 01:29:51,280
你
Who

1452
01:29:51,910 --> 01:29:55,370
以为你是谁啊
in the hell do you think you are?

1453
01:29:55,370 --> 01:29:57,290
你杀了我母亲
You killed my mother!

1454
01:29:57,290 --> 01:29:58,580
我
I tried...

1455
01:29:58,580 --> 01:30:00,260
那么努力
so hard...

1456
01:30:00,500 --> 01:30:04,210
找到最适合你的形态
to find the form that best suited you...

1457
01:30:04,590 --> 01:30:07,400
这就是你的感谢吗
and this is the thanks I get?

1458
01:30:07,740 --> 01:30:10,860
你真得长大了
You really need to grow up.

1459
01:30:15,090 --> 01:30:17,070
我本想跟你一起做的
I wanted to do this together...

1460
01:30:17,620 --> 01:30:19,270
但看来你只能
but I suppose you'll have to learn

1461
01:30:19,280 --> 01:30:22,700
做个一千年的电池  慢慢长进了
by spending the next thousand years as a battery!

1462
01:30:24,900 --> 01:30:26,690
可算  火箭
Finally! Rocket?

1463
01:30:26,690 --> 01:30:29,390
把发射器带在身边  我好找你
Keep that transmitter nearby, so I can find you.

1464
01:30:29,390 --> 01:30:31,450
我们在一件旧施工设备里
We're in an old piece of construction equipment

1465
01:30:31,450 --> 01:30:34,580
勇度曾用它来切开艾斯克维拉银行
Yondu once used to slice open the Bank of A'askavaria.

1466
01:30:34,580 --> 01:30:35,570
伊戈是个疯子
Ego's unhinged.

1467
01:30:35,570 --> 01:30:36,990
我知道  准备好
I know. Get ready.

1468
01:30:36,990 --> 01:30:38,400
放  克拉林
Drop her, Kraglin.

1469
01:30:56,850 --> 01:30:58,090
不
No.

1470
01:31:09,310 --> 01:31:12,330
我的生命  我的爱
My life, my love.

1471
01:31:12,460 --> 01:31:14,760
我的女人是大海
My lady is the sea

1472
01:31:16,750 --> 01:31:17,620
彼得
Peter...

1473
01:31:18,660 --> 01:31:20,910
这就是那海
this is the sea.

1474
01:32:03,930 --> 01:32:05,820
你好啊  混蛋
Hey, there, jackass!

1475
01:32:15,850 --> 01:32:17,440
那是什么玩意
What is that thing?

1476
01:32:24,900 --> 01:32:27,250
闪开  小笨格鲁特
Out of the way, dumber, smaller Groot!

1477
01:32:31,810 --> 01:32:34,190
我就说有点不对劲
I told you something didn't feel right.

1478
01:32:34,630 --> 01:32:36,850
"我早说过"  我现在正需要听这种话
"I told you so." Just what I need to hear right now.

1479
01:32:36,850 --> 01:32:38,430
我不是回来了吗
Well, I came back, didn't I?

1480
01:32:39,320 --> 01:32:40,620
因为我们有心照不宣的情愫
Because there's an unspoken thing.

1481
01:32:40,620 --> 01:32:42,840
才没有什么心照不宣的情愫
There is no unspoken thing.

1482
01:32:42,840 --> 01:32:45,260
你干什么呢  你差点害死我们
What are you doing? You could've killed us all!

1483
01:32:45,750 --> 01:32:47,050
"谢谢  火箭"
"Thank you, Rocket"?

1484
01:32:47,050 --> 01:32:48,430
我们都控制局面了
We had it under control.

1485
01:32:48,430 --> 01:32:52,120
我们没有  那只是他真身的延伸
We did not. That is only an extension of his true self.

1486
01:32:52,120 --> 01:32:53,400
他很快就会回来的
He will be back soon.

1487
01:32:53,400 --> 01:32:54,470
蓝妹妹怎么在这儿
What's Smurfette doing here?

1488
01:32:54,470 --> 01:32:56,560
我只想搭车回家
Whatever I need to do to get a damn ride home.

1489
01:32:56,560 --> 01:32:58,200
她还想杀我
She tried to murder me!

1490
01:32:58,200 --> 01:33:00,200
我救了你  你个蠢狐狸
I saved you, you stupid fox!

1491
01:33:00,200 --> 01:33:01,670
他不是狐狸
He's not a fox.

1492
01:33:01,670 --> 01:33:03,750
-我是格鲁特  -我也不是浣兔
- I am Groot. - I'm not a raboon, either.

1493
01:33:03,750 --> 01:33:05,030
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1494
01:33:05,030 --> 01:33:06,800
是"浣熊"  算了
"Raccoon." Whatever.

1495
01:33:09,990 --> 01:33:11,580
怎么杀一个天神啊
How do we kill a Celestial?

1496
01:33:11,580 --> 01:33:12,990
他有个核
There's a center to him.

1497
01:33:13,000 --> 01:33:15,370
他的大脑还是灵魂什么的
His brain, his soul, whatever it is...

1498
01:33:15,370 --> 01:33:17,060
有个保护壳
Some sort of protective shell.

1499
01:33:17,060 --> 01:33:19,640
在地表下的洞穴里
It's in the caverns below the surface.

1500
01:33:21,900 --> 01:33:22,910
勇度
Yondu?

1501
01:33:32,070 --> 01:33:33,580
推进器失去动力了
Thrusters are out.

1502
01:33:33,580 --> 01:33:35,480
看来我该庆幸我长得瘦
Guess I should be glad I was a skinny kid.

1503
01:33:35,490 --> 01:33:37,740
否则你就会把我交给这个疯子了
Otherwise, you'd have delivered me to this maniac.

1504
01:33:37,740 --> 01:33:40,280
你还以为那是我留下了你的原因吗  白痴
You still reckon that's the reason I kept you around, you idiot?

1505
01:33:40,280 --> 01:33:42,340
是你这么跟我说的  你个老笨蛋
That's what you told me, you old doofus.

1506
01:33:42,340 --> 01:33:44,600
我搞明白了其他孩子的下场后
Once I figured out what happened to them other kids

1507
01:33:44,600 --> 01:33:46,320
我当然不能把你交出去
I wasn't just gonna hand you over.

1508
01:33:46,320 --> 01:33:48,280
你说你要吃了我
You said you were gonna eat me.

1509
01:33:48,280 --> 01:33:50,050
那是玩笑话
That was being funny!

1510
01:33:50,520 --> 01:33:51,650
我可没想笑
Not to me!

1511
01:33:51,650 --> 01:33:53,230
你们真有毛病
You people have issues.

1512
01:33:53,230 --> 01:33:55,350
我当然有毛病
Of course I have issues.

1513
01:33:55,750 --> 01:33:58,260
那可是我老爸
That's my freakin' father!

1514
01:33:58,630 --> 01:34:00,340
推进器恢复了
Thrusters are back up.

1515
01:34:13,940 --> 01:34:16,200
-我们该向上飞  -不行
- We should be going up! - We can't!

1516
01:34:16,200 --> 01:34:19,200
伊戈想毁掉我们所知的宇宙
Ego wants to eradicate the universe as we know it.

1517
01:34:19,200 --> 01:34:20,370
我们得杀了他
We have to kill him.

1518
01:34:20,370 --> 01:34:21,290
火箭
Rocket!

1519
01:34:21,290 --> 01:34:22,170
好嘞
Got it!

1520
01:34:36,260 --> 01:34:38,250
那我们又要拯救银河系了
So, we're saving the galaxy again?

1521
01:34:38,300 --> 01:34:39,330
大概是吧
I guess.

1522
01:34:39,520 --> 01:34:40,500
太棒了
Awesome!

1523
01:34:42,860 --> 01:34:44,820
如果我们救了两次银河系
We're really gonna be able to jack up our prices

1524
01:34:44,820 --> 01:34:46,750
就能坐地起价了
if we're two-time galaxy savers.

1525
01:34:46,750 --> 01:34:49,470
我真不敢相信你居然想到了这个
I seriously can't believe that's where your mind goes.

1526
01:34:49,470 --> 01:34:52,330
就是想想嘛  哥们  我们不是朋友嘛
It was just a random thought, man. I thought we were friends.

1527
01:34:52,340 --> 01:34:54,830
我当然在乎那些星球啊  建筑啊
Of course, I care about the planets, and the buildings

1528
01:34:54,830 --> 01:34:56,950
和各个星球上的动物啊
and all the animals on the planets.

1529
01:34:56,950 --> 01:34:58,250
还有人呢
And the people.

1530
01:34:59,430 --> 01:35:03,850
那个坏脾气狗狗好可爱  他让我想死
The crabby puppy is so cute. He makes me wanna die!

1531
01:35:41,790 --> 01:35:42,860
飞行员
Pilots...

1532
01:35:42,920 --> 01:35:44,620
释放先遣队
release envoy units.

1533
01:35:46,300 --> 01:35:50,190
我们的传感器感应到电池在星球地表下
Our sensors detect the batteries are below the surface of the planet.

1534
01:35:52,390 --> 01:35:53,390
下潜
Dive!

1535
01:36:11,250 --> 01:36:12,150
船长
Captain?

1536
01:36:12,630 --> 01:36:13,440
船长
Captain?

1537
01:36:19,180 --> 01:36:21,180
伊戈为什么找你来
Tell me why Ego wants you here?

1538
01:36:21,240 --> 01:36:23,480
他需要我跟光的基因联系
He needs my genetic connection to the light

1539
01:36:23,480 --> 01:36:25,270
来帮他毁灭宇宙
to help destroy the universe.

1540
01:36:25,270 --> 01:36:27,480
他还想教我控制能量
He tried to teach me how to control the power.

1541
01:36:27,660 --> 01:36:28,790
你能控制吗
So, could you?

1542
01:36:29,180 --> 01:36:30,030
稍稍能吧
A little.

1543
01:36:30,420 --> 01:36:31,530
我做了个能量球
I made a ball.

1544
01:36:31,880 --> 01:36:32,930
球
A ball?

1545
01:36:33,140 --> 01:36:34,900
我已经拼命去想了
I thought as hard as I could.

1546
01:36:34,900 --> 01:36:36,510
我只能弄出来个那个
It was all that I could come up with.

1547
01:36:36,510 --> 01:36:37,590
你"想"
You "thought"?

1548
01:36:37,900 --> 01:36:39,660
你以为我控制这支箭飞的时候
You think when I make this arrow fly

1549
01:36:39,660 --> 01:36:41,130
是用的脑袋吗
I use my head?

1550
01:37:04,060 --> 01:37:04,820
那儿
There.

1551
01:37:04,820 --> 01:37:06,530
那就是伊戈的核
That's Ego's core.

1552
01:37:09,100 --> 01:37:10,890
外壳很厚  火箭
That ore is thick, Rocket.

1553
01:37:10,930 --> 01:37:12,280
交给我吧
I got it covered.

1554
01:37:18,650 --> 01:37:20,020
我们必须快点
We must hurry.

1555
01:37:20,090 --> 01:37:22,640
伊戈很快就会找到我们
It will not take Ego long to find us.

1556
01:37:26,680 --> 01:37:27,930
稳住
Keep it steady.

1557
01:37:34,270 --> 01:37:36,600
钻透到核  然后杀死他
We drill into the center, we kill him!

1558
01:37:43,530 --> 01:37:44,450
船长
Captain?

1559
01:37:44,500 --> 01:37:45,820
怎么了  克拉林
What is it, Kraglin?

1560
01:37:46,200 --> 01:37:48,220
还记得阿耶莎那妞儿吗
Remember that Ayesha chick?

1561
01:37:48,220 --> 01:37:49,320
记得  怎么了
Yeah, why?

1562
01:37:50,030 --> 01:37:51,090
该死
Oh, hell!

1563
01:38:12,350 --> 01:38:14,190
你为什么不开激光炮
Why aren't you firing the lasers?

1564
01:38:14,190 --> 01:38:16,100
