I think I packed a small detonator.

1566
01:38:18,450 --> 01:38:20,670
有引爆器没炸药也没用
A detonator is worthless without explosives.

1567
01:38:20,680 --> 01:38:22,400
我们有这些
Well, we got these.

1568
01:38:22,910 --> 01:38:25,030
这玩意的破坏性能杀死伊戈吗
Is that thing strong enough to kill Ego?

1569
01:38:25,040 --> 01:38:27,210
如果能的话  会造成他整个
If it is, it'll cause a chain reaction

1570
01:38:27,210 --> 01:38:29,070
神经系统的连锁反应
throughout his entire nervous system.

1571
01:38:29,080 --> 01:38:29,860
意思是
Meaning what?

1572
01:38:29,860 --> 01:38:31,880
整颗星球都会爆炸
The entire planet will explode.

1573
01:38:31,880 --> 01:38:33,810
我们得快点逃出去
We'll have to get out of here fast.

1574
01:38:33,810 --> 01:38:35,290
我装了个定时器
I rigged a timer.

1575
01:38:36,110 --> 01:38:36,910
走
Go!

1576
01:38:51,170 --> 01:38:52,890
他要来了
He's coming.

1577
01:38:54,630 --> 01:38:56,350
你不是说你能让他睡着吗
Didn't you say you could make him sleep?

1578
01:38:56,710 --> 01:38:59,330
在他想睡的时候  他太强大了
When he wants. He's too powerful.

1579
01:38:59,330 --> 01:39:00,600
我做不到
I can't!

1580
01:39:01,130 --> 01:39:02,980
你不用相信自己
You don't have to believe in yourself

1581
01:39:03,320 --> 01:39:05,640
因为我相信你
because I believe in you.

1582
01:39:17,910 --> 01:39:19,310
睡吧
Sleep!

1583
01:39:26,310 --> 01:39:28,090
我没想到她能做到
I never thought she'd be able to do it

1584
01:39:28,270 --> 01:39:30,510
毕竟她一副很瘦弱的样子
with as weak and skinny as she appears to be.

1585
01:39:31,430 --> 01:39:33,950
我不知道我能拖住他多久
I don't know how long I can hold him.

1586
01:39:37,620 --> 01:39:39,080
金属太厚了
The metal's too thick.

1587
01:39:39,080 --> 01:39:40,200
要让炸弹达到目的
For the bomb to work,

1588
01:39:40,200 --> 01:39:43,110
我们得把它放在伊戈的核上
we'd actually need to place it on Ego's core.

1589
01:39:43,110 --> 01:39:46,060
我们的大屁股钻不进这些小洞里
And our fat butts ain't gonna fit through those tiny holes.

1590
01:39:46,060 --> 01:39:47,320
那么
Well...

1591
01:39:49,830 --> 01:39:51,390
这主意糟透了
That's a terrible idea.

1592
01:39:51,430 --> 01:39:54,010
我们就剩这一个主意了
Which is the only kind of idea we have left.

1593
01:39:54,700 --> 01:39:56,400
难以置信
Unbelievable.

1594
01:39:56,400 --> 01:39:59,450
"火箭  做这个  火箭  做那个"
"Rocket, do this. Rocket, do that."

1595
01:40:00,470 --> 01:40:01,670
今天真够受的
What a day.

1596
01:40:09,490 --> 01:40:12,970
好了  首先你打开这个开关  再打开这个
All right, first you flick this switch, then this switch.

1597
01:40:12,970 --> 01:40:14,500
这样就启动了
That activates it.

1598
01:40:14,500 --> 01:40:16,770
接着你按下这个按钮
Then you push this button

1599
01:40:16,780 --> 01:40:19,530
让你有五分钟时间逃跑
which will give you five minutes to get out of there.

1600
01:40:19,910 --> 01:40:21,550
不管你做什么
Now, whatever you do

1601
01:40:21,550 --> 01:40:24,130
千万别按这个按钮
don't push this button

1602
01:40:24,130 --> 01:40:26,360
因为那样会立即引爆炸弹
because that will set off the bomb immediately

1603
01:40:26,360 --> 01:40:27,910
我们就都没命了
and we'll all be dead.

1604
01:40:27,910 --> 01:40:30,530
重复一遍我刚才说的
Now, repeat back what I just said.

1605
01:40:30,860 --> 01:40:32,280
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1606
01:40:32,700 --> 01:40:34,790
-我是格鲁特  -对了
- I am Groot. - That's right.

1607
01:40:34,790 --> 01:40:36,390
-我是格鲁特  -不
- I am Groot. - No!

1608
01:40:36,390 --> 01:40:38,720
不对  这个按钮会杀死所有人
No, that's the button that will kill everyone!

1609
01:40:39,130 --> 01:40:40,180
再来
Try again.

1610
01:40:42,940 --> 01:40:44,060
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1611
01:40:44,900 --> 01:40:46,120
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1612
01:40:47,410 --> 01:40:48,060
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1613
01:40:48,060 --> 01:40:50,020
不  你刚才就是这么错的
No! That's exactly what you just said!

1614
01:40:50,020 --> 01:40:51,870
这怎么可能
How is that even possible?

1615
01:40:51,880 --> 01:40:53,910
你应该按哪个按钮
Which button is the button you're supposed to push?

1616
01:40:53,910 --> 01:40:55,000
指一下
Point to it.

1617
01:40:55,860 --> 01:40:57,030
不对
No!

1618
01:40:57,100 --> 01:40:58,670
你让他紧张了
You're making him nervous!

1619
01:40:58,670 --> 01:41:00,570
闭嘴  给我拿点胶带来
Shut up and get me some tape!

1620
01:41:00,570 --> 01:41:02,220
外面有人有胶带吗
Does anybody have any tape out there?

1621
01:41:02,220 --> 01:41:03,990
我要把死亡按钮贴上胶带
I wanna put some tape over the death button.

1622
01:41:04,000 --> 01:41:06,320
我没胶带  我去问问
I don't have any tape. Let me check.

1623
01:41:07,170 --> 01:41:09,590
勇度  你有...
Yo, Yondu... do you have...

1624
01:41:10,040 --> 01:41:12,130
你有胶带吗
Do you have any tape?

1625
01:41:14,520 --> 01:41:17,000
卡魔拉  你有胶带吗
Gamora? Do you have any tape?

1626
01:41:17,700 --> 01:41:18,530
胶带
Tape!

1627
