没人有胶带
Nobody has any tape!

1633
01:41:33,720 --> 01:41:35,830
谁都没有胶带吗
Not a single person has tape?

1634
01:41:35,830 --> 01:41:36,430
没有
Nope!

1635
01:41:36,430 --> 01:41:38,140
你问过星云了吗
Did you ask Nebula?

1636
01:41:38,910 --> 01:41:39,600
问过了
Yes!

1637
01:41:39,600 --> 01:41:40,800
你确定吗
Are you sure?

1638
