Guardians...

1648
01:42:26,310 --> 01:42:28,420
也许这对你们会是个安慰
perhaps it will provide you solace

1649
01:42:28,420 --> 01:42:31,040
你们的死  不会毫无意义
that your deaths are not without purpose.

1650
01:42:31,330 --> 01:42:32,900
而是会警告那些
They will serve as a warning

1651
01:42:32,910 --> 01:42:35,380
想要背叛我们的人
to all of those tempted with betraying us.

1652
01:42:36,100 --> 01:42:38,870
别想耍索维林族
Don't screw with the Sovereign.

1653
01:42:42,740 --> 01:42:43,940
会很疼的
This is gonna hurt.

1654
01:42:43,940 --> 01:42:45,500
光说不练
Promises, promises.

1655
01:43:08,300 --> 01:43:09,140
不
No!

1656
01:43:09,770 --> 01:43:13,730
不不不
No! No! No!

1657
01:43:17,220 --> 01:43:18,580
要爆炸了
We're gonna blow!

1658
01:43:23,890 --> 01:43:26,230
彼得  不
Peter! No!

1659
01:43:45,730 --> 01:43:46,540
怎么了
What?

1660
01:43:47,170 --> 01:43:48,900
你活像玛丽·波平斯
You look like Mary Poppins.

1661
01:43:49,310 --> 01:43:50,490
他酷吗
Is he cool?

1662
01:43:52,300 --> 01:43:53,690
当然  他很酷
Hell, yeah, he's cool.

1663
01:43:54,750 --> 01:43:56,570
我是玛丽·波平斯哦
I'm Mary Poppins, y'all!

1664
01:44:24,070 --> 01:44:25,740
螳螂  小心
Mantis, look out!

1665
01:44:37,960 --> 01:44:39,500
她只是昏过去了
She's just unconscious.

1666
01:44:55,720 --> 01:44:57,210
炸弹还有多久炸
How long until the bomb goes off?

1667
01:44:57,210 --> 01:44:59,960
万一万一格鲁特没把我们都炸死
In the unlikely event that Groot doesn't kill us all...

1668
01:45:00,110 --> 01:45:01,490
那还有六分钟
about six minutes.

1669
01:45:06,130 --> 01:45:08,890
克拉林  我们需要飞行舱来带我们撤离
Kraglin, we need the quadrant for an extraction.

1670
01:45:08,900 --> 01:45:09,670
倒计时5分钟
T-minus five minutes.

1671
01:45:09,670 --> 01:45:10,740
是  船长
Aye, Captain.

1672
01:45:14,810 --> 01:45:17,680
克拉林到时  上面得有人接应
Somebody's gotta be up top when Kraglin arrives.

1673
01:45:18,200 --> 01:45:19,990
德拉克斯  带螳螂走
Drax, take Mantis.

1674
01:45:22,590 --> 01:45:23,930
我的乳头
My nipples!

1675
01:45:31,830 --> 01:45:33,010
卡魔拉
Gamora!

1676
01:45:37,070 --> 01:45:38,260
彼得
Peter!

1677
01:46:04,340 --> 01:46:05,700
别想多了
Get over it.

1678
01:46:05,870 --> 01:46:09,700
得了  彼得  我知道你并不想这样
Come now, Peter. I know this isn't what you want.

1679
01:46:12,080 --> 01:46:16,650
我让你做出这样的选择  还算什么父亲啊
What kind of father would I be to let you make this choice?

1680
01:46:46,210 --> 01:46:47,260
帅气
Yeah!

1681
01:46:48,310 --> 01:46:52,210
很快  彼得  我们就将成为一切
Soon, Peter, we will be all there is.

1682
01:46:52,320 --> 01:46:56,060
