I don't want to do this alone.

1687
01:49:34,690 --> 01:49:36,340
你不能拒绝
You cannot deny

1688
01:49:36,340 --> 01:49:40,380
宇宙赋予你的人生目的
the purpose the universe has bestowed upon you.

1689
01:49:49,250 --> 01:49:51,600
大家不要靠近
Everyone, I need you to stay back!

1690
01:49:51,660 --> 01:49:52,860
那是什么
What is that?

1691
01:50:08,170 --> 01:50:10,490
不非得如此的  彼得
It doesn't need to be like this, Peter.

1692
01:50:11,990 --> 01:50:15,040
你为什么要毁掉我们的机会
Why are you destroying our chance?

1693
01:50:18,130 --> 01:50:21,080
别再否认自己的身份了
Stop pretending you aren't what you are.

1694
01:50:23,320 --> 01:50:24,770
你是上亿
One in billions.

1695
01:50:25,820 --> 01:50:27,840
上兆  甚至更多中的唯一
Trillions. Even more.

1696
01:50:30,120 --> 01:50:34,790
生命怎么可能有更伟大的意义
What greater meaning can life possibly have to offer?

1697
01:50:37,220 --> 01:50:41,310
我不是用脑袋控制箭的  孩子
I don't use my head to fly the arrow, boy!

1698
01:50:41,870 --> 01:50:43,920
我是用心
I use my heart...

1699
01:51:18,890 --> 01:51:22,690
你不该杀了我妈妈  还捏碎我的随身听
You shouldn't have killed my mom, and squished my Walkman.

1700
01:52:03,060 --> 01:52:06,080
格鲁特  如果你听得到  快点
Groot? If you can hear me, hurry up!

1701
01:52:06,080 --> 01:52:09,330
我不确定奎尔还能分散他注意力多久
I'm not sure how long Quill can keep him distracted!

1702
01:52:09,660 --> 01:52:10,850
格鲁特  快点
Groot, hurry!

1703
01:53:07,020 --> 01:53:09,340
勇度  我们要炸了
Yondu, we're about to blow!

1704
01:53:09,340 --> 01:53:10,750
上船
Get to the ship!

1705
01:53:10,930 --> 01:53:12,220
不能丢下奎尔
Not without Quill!

1706
01:53:12,220 --> 01:53:14,450
你还得照顾小树枝
You need to take care of the twig!

1707
01:53:15,620 --> 01:53:17,340
不能丢下你
Not without you!

1708
01:53:18,580 --> 01:53:21,720
我这辈子都没做过几件好事  耗子
I ain't done nothin' right my whole damn life, rat.

1709
01:53:25,300 --> 01:53:26,970
让我做这件吧
You need to give me this.

1710
01:53:37,690 --> 01:53:39,880
一套太空服和一个飞行装置
A spacesuit and an aero-rig.

1711
01:53:40,290 --> 01:53:41,890
我一样只有一个
I only have one of each.

1712
01:53:54,790 --> 01:53:56,710
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1713
01:53:57,210 --> 01:53:58,310
他说什么
What's that?

1714
01:54:00,060 --> 01:54:04,310
他说  "欢迎加入他娘的银河护卫队"
He says, "Welcome to the frickin' Guardians of the Galaxy."

1715
01:54:04,780 --> 01:54:06,890
而且他用的词不是"他娘的"
Only he didn't use "Frickin'."

1716
01:54:13,380 --> 01:54:14,490
再见  小树枝
Bye, twig.

1717
01:54:16,390 --> 01:54:19,350
我们回头得好好谈谈你说粗话的问题
We're gonna need to have a real discussion about your language.

1718
01:55:14,690 --> 01:55:15,670
彼得呢
Where's Peter?

1719
01:55:16,480 --> 01:55:17,910
火箭  他在哪
Rocket, where is he?

1720
01:55:19,240 --> 01:55:20,100
火箭
Rocket.

1721
01:55:20,300 --> 01:55:22,040
火箭  看着我  他在哪
Rocket, look at me! Where is he?

1722
01:55:28,240 --> 01:55:30,790
不  我不能丢下他
No. I'm not leaving without him.

1723
01:55:37,710 --> 01:55:38,780
对不起
I'm sorry.

1724
01:55:39,590 --> 01:55:41,910
我今天只能承受失去一个朋友
I can only afford to lose one friend today.

1725
01:55:42,930 --> 01:55:44,440
克拉林  走
Kraglin, go!

1726
01:55:44,550 --> 01:55:45,360
等等
Wait...

1727
01:55:46,470 --> 01:55:47,510
奎尔回来了吗
Is Quill back?

1728
01:55:49,600 --> 01:55:51,600
火箭  奎尔呢
Rocket, where's Quill?

1729
01:55:53,040 --> 01:55:55,950
火箭  奎尔呢
Rocket, where's Quill?

1730
01:55:57,480 --> 01:55:58,430
火箭
Rocket!

1731
01:56:00,100 --> 01:56:01,580
奎尔呢
Where's Quill?

1732
01:56:03,040 --> 01:56:04,600
奎尔呢
Where's Quill?

1733
01:56:13,040 --> 01:56:14,720
不  我们得阻止它
No, we need to stop it.

1734
01:56:14,730 --> 01:56:16,210
我们得阻止它
We need to stop it.

1735
01:56:19,460 --> 01:56:21,380
不  停下
No. Stop.

1736
01:56:22,100 --> 01:56:23,990
停下  听着  听我说
Stop. Listen. Listen to me!

1737
01:56:24,190 --> 01:56:25,730
你是个神
You are a god.

1738
01:56:26,790 --> 01:56:28,090
如果你杀了我
If you kill me...

1739
01:56:28,590 --> 01:56:30,990
你就跟其他人一样了
you'll be just like everybody else.

1740
01:56:32,210 --> 01:56:34,090
那有什么不好
What's so wrong with that?

1741
01:56:34,260 --> 01:56:35,440
不
No!

1742
01:57:25,690 --> 01:57:29,530
他或许是你生父  孩子  但他可不是你爸爸
He may have been your father, boy, but he wasn't your daddy.

1743
01:57:33,800 --> 01:57:36,050
真抱歉我一件事都没做对
I'm sorry I didn't do none of it right.

1744
01:57:37,150 --> 01:57:39,050
你是我的孩子我太走运了
I'm damn lucky you're my boy.

1745
01:57:43,180 --> 01:57:44,080
什么
What?

1746
01:57:56,480 --> 01:57:57,810
勇度  你干什么
Yondu, what are you doing?

1747
01:57:57,940 --> 01:57:58,900
不行
You can't.

1748
01:58:00,460 --> 01:58:01,670
勇度
Yondu!

1749
01:58:06,910 --> 01:58:07,750
不
No!

1750
01:58:08,490 --> 01:58:09,270
不
No!

1751
01:58:13,150 --> 01:58:14,110
不
No!

1752
01:58:17,350 --> 01:58:20,010
不不
No! No!

1753
01:58:21,300 --> 01:58:22,740
不要
No!

1754
01:59:17,260 --> 01:59:18,850
我告诉卡魔拉
I told Gamora

1755
01:59:18,850 --> 01:59:19,960
我小时候
how when I was a kid

1756
01:59:19,960 --> 01:59:23,030
会假装大卫·霍索夫是我爸爸
I used to pretend David Hasselhoff was my dad.

1757
01:59:25,050 --> 01:59:28,090
他是地球的一个歌手演员  很出名
He's a singer and actor from Earth, really famous guy.

1758
01:59:29,970 --> 01:59:31,510
刚刚  我突然想到
Earlier, it struck me...

1759
01:59:32,750 --> 01:59:37,060
勇度没有会说话的车  但他有会飞的箭
Yondu didn't have a talking car, but he did have a flying arrow.

1760
01:59:37,740 --> 01:59:39,820
他没有天使般美丽的歌喉
He didn't have the beautiful voice of an angel

1761
01:59:39,830 --> 01:59:41,930
但他的哨声有如天籁
but he did have the whistle of one.

1762
01:59:42,470 --> 01:59:46,070
勇度和大卫·霍索夫都会经历牛逼的冒险
Both Yondu and David Hasselhoff went on kick-ass adventures

1763
01:59:46,070 --> 01:59:47,790
勾搭性感的女人
and hooked up with hot women

1764
01:59:48,800 --> 01:59:50,420
还打机器人
and fought robots.

1765
01:59:53,370 --> 01:59:56,780
看来大卫·霍索夫终究成为了我爸爸
I guess David Hasselhoff did kind of end up being my dad after all.

1766
01:59:57,900 --> 01:59:59,450
但其实那是你  勇度
Only it was you, Yondu.

1767
02:00:05,370 --> 02:00:06,760
我有个很酷的爸爸
I had a pretty cool dad.

1768
02:00:10,240 --> 02:00:11,950
我想说的是
What I'm trying to say here is...

1769
02:00:13,840 --> 02:00:18,570
有时候你寻找了一生的东西
sometimes that thing you're searching for your whole life

1770
02:00:20,970 --> 02:00:22,900
其实一直在你身边
it's right there by your side all along.

1771
02:00:23,540 --> 02:00:24,810
你却不自知
You don't even know it.

1772
02:00:37,320 --> 02:00:38,650
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1773
02:00:40,210 --> 02:00:41,790
他是喊你小树枝
He did call you twig.

1774
02:00:44,350 --> 02:00:45,370
星云
Nebula...

1775
02:00:50,640 --> 02:00:52,260
我跟你一样只是个孩子
I was a child like you.

1776
02:00:53,590 --> 02:00:57,440
我每天只想着活到第二天
I was concerned with staying alive until the next day, every day.

1777
02:00:57,720 --> 02:01:00,190
我从未想过灭霸对你做了什么
And I never considered what Thanos was doing to you.

1778
02:01:00,970 --> 02:01:02,310
我想弥补
I'm trying to make it right.

1779
02:01:02,950 --> 02:01:05,570
整个宇宙中还有其他你这样的小女孩
There are little girls like you across the universe

1780
02:01:05,580 --> 02:01:07,110
她们有危险
who are in danger.

1781
02:01:09,460 --> 02:01:11,330
你可以留下  跟我们一起帮助她们
You can stay with us and help them.

1782
02:01:12,110 --> 02:01:14,370
我杀了灭霸就能帮助她们
I will help them by killing Thanos.

1783
02:01:14,670 --> 02:01:16,160
我不知道那是否能做到
I don't know if that's possible.

1784
02:01:31,510 --> 02:01:33,320
你永远是我妹妹
You will always be my sister.

1785
02:02:18,180 --> 02:02:19,000
彼得
Pete!

1786
02:02:22,680 --> 02:02:24,360
船长在一家旧货店为你找到了这个
Captain found this for you in a junker shop.

1787
02:02:24,370 --> 02:02:26,590
说你有一天会回来的
Said you'd come back to the fold someday.

1788
02:02:29,210 --> 02:02:30,080
是什么
What is it?

1789
02:02:30,390 --> 02:02:31,170
叫Zune
It's called a Zune.

1790
02:02:31,170 --> 02:02:33,680
地球人现在都听这玩意了
It's what everybody's listening to on Earth nowadays.

1791
02:02:33,680 --> 02:02:35,050
里面能存300首歌
It's got 300 songs on it.

1792
02:02:35,050 --> 02:02:37,280
300首歌
300 songs?

1793
02:02:42,580 --> 02:02:43,370
等等
Wait.

1794
02:02:49,830 --> 02:02:51,690
火箭把残片捡走  重拼了起来
Rocket grabbed the pieces, and reassembled them.

1795
02:02:51,690 --> 02:02:53,830
我觉得勇度会希望留给你的
I think Yondu would want you to have it.

1796
02:02:57,650 --> 02:02:58,600
谢谢
Thanks...

1797
02:03:00,920 --> 02:03:01,760
船长
Captain.

1798
02:04:14,250 --> 02:04:15,420
他们来了
They came.

1799
02:04:23,560 --> 02:04:24,630
是什么
What is it?

1800
02:04:25,660 --> 02:04:28,330
我给勇度以前的掠夺者朋友去了消息
I sent word to Yondu's old Ravager buddies,

1801
02:04:28,330 --> 02:04:29,880
把他做的事告诉了他们
and told them what he did.

1802
02:04:33,380 --> 02:04:35,010
这是掠夺者的葬礼
It's a Ravager funeral.

1803
02:04:52,660 --> 02:04:54,280
好啊
Yeah!

1804
02:04:54,290 --> 02:04:55,610
好
Yeah!

1805
02:05:03,070 --> 02:05:05,100
他终究没有辜负我们  船长
He didn't let us down after all, Captain.

1806
02:05:05,800 --> 02:05:07,460
是啊  孩子
No, he did not, son.

1807
02:05:08,820 --> 02:05:10,270
他没有
He did not.

1808
02:05:17,010 --> 02:05:20,440
永别了  老朋友
Fare thee well, old friend.

1809
02:05:22,720 --> 02:05:26,880
勇度·尤冬塔  我们在群星中再会
Yondu Udonta, I will see you in the stars.

1810
02:05:31,290 --> 02:05:32,940
他没把他们赶走
He didn't chase them away.

1811
02:05:33,480 --> 02:05:34,310
是啊
No.

1812
02:05:35,570 --> 02:05:37,280
虽然他吼他们
Even though he yelled at them.

1813
02:05:38,350 --> 02:05:39,850
总那么尖酸
And was always mean.

1814
02:05:42,180 --> 02:05:44,340
还偷了他用不着的电池
And he stole batteries he didn't need.

1815
02:05:49,660 --> 02:05:51,030
当然不会了
Well, of course not.

1816
02:06:15,650 --> 02:06:16,420
怎么了
What?

1817
02:06:17,550 --> 02:06:18,650
就是
It's just...

1818
02:06:21,230 --> 02:06:23,230
心照不宣的情愫
some unspoken thing.

1819
02:06:33,080 --> 02:06:34,690
真美
It's beautiful.

1820
02:06:36,680 --> 02:06:37,550
是啊
It is.

1821
02:06:39,400 --> 02:06:40,520
你也很美
And so are you.

1822
02:06:43,410 --> 02:06:44,610
内在美
On the inside.

1823
02:08:39,980 --> 02:08:41,480
真是遗憾
You know, it's a shame...

1824
02:08:41,820 --> 02:08:44,350
要失去勇度这样的惨剧
that it took the tragedy of losing Yondu

1825
02:08:44,350 --> 02:08:46,180
才让我们重聚
to bring us all together again.

1826
02:08:46,530 --> 02:08:48,380
但我觉得如果他知道我们重新组队
But I think he'd be proud knowing that

1827
02:08:48,380 --> 02:08:50,230
一定会骄傲的
we are back as a team.

1828
02:08:50,550 --> 02:08:51,500
我加入
I'm in.

1829
02:08:51,590 --> 02:08:52,370
太好了
Dope.

1830
02:08:52,380 --> 02:08:54,750
我想死你们了
I miss you guys so much!

1831
02:08:54,750 --> 02:08:56,220
太好了
Hell, yes.

1832
02:08:59,070 --> 02:09:00,950
我们去偷点东西吧
What say we steal some shit?

1833
02:11:20,290 --> 02:11:22,850
大祭司  理事会在等您
High Priestess, the Council is waiting.

1834
02:11:23,530 --> 02:11:26,390
他们不满我浪费了资源
They are perturbed I've wasted our resources.

1835
02:11:31,160 --> 02:11:32,960
等他们看到了我的创造
When they see what I have created here

1836
02:11:32,960 --> 02:11:35,140
他们的愤怒就会消散
their wrath will dissipate.

1837
02:11:37,650 --> 02:11:40,630
是新型生育荚吗  夫人
It's a new type of birthing pod, ma'am?

1838
02:11:41,440 --> 02:11:42,990
好孩子  那个
That, my child

1839
02:11:43,420 --> 02:11:45,340
是我们进化的下一步
is the next step in our evolution.

1840
02:11:45,570 --> 02:11:48,010
更强大  更美丽
More powerful, more beautiful,

1841
02:11:48,770 --> 02:11:52,560
更有能力摧毁银河护卫队
more capable of destroying the Guardians of the Galaxy.

1842
02:11:55,540 --> 02:11:57,250
我就叫他
I think I shall call him...

1843
02:11:59,790 --> 02:12:00,720
亚当吧
Adam.

1844
02:14:04,050 --> 02:14:04,930
哥们
Dude.

1845
02:14:05,520 --> 02:14:06,690
不是吧
Seriously?

1846
02:14:06,690 --> 02:14:09,360
你得清理你的房间  简直乱成一团
You gotta clean up your room. It's a complete mess.

1847
02:14:09,370 --> 02:14:10,830
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1848
02:14:10,830 --> 02:14:13,000
我才不无聊  你才无聊
I am not boring. You're boring.

1849
02:14:13,000 --> 02:14:13,960
你知道什么无聊吗
You know what's boring?

1850
02:14:13,960 --> 02:14:17,390
坐在那里  玩那个没劲的游戏
Sitting there, playing that mind-numbing game.

1851
02:14:17,390 --> 02:14:21,110
无聊的是我每天要被你的藤蔓绊倒
What's boring is me tripping over your vines every day!

1852
02:14:21,520 --> 02:14:22,820
我才不无聊
I'm not boring!

1853
02:14:22,890 --> 02:14:24,940
我是格鲁特
I am Groot.

1854
02:14:25,560 --> 02:14:27,400
现在我能体会勇度当年的心情了
And now I know how Yondu felt.

1855
02:15:03,710 --> 02:15:05,840
在这艰难时期
In these times of hardship...

1856
02:15:07,300 --> 02:15:08,680
记住
just remember...

1857
02:15:09,700 --> 02:15:14,020
我们是格鲁特
We. Are. Groot.

1858
02:15:17,250 --> 02:15:18,390
伙计们
Hey, fellas.

1859
02:15:18,520 --> 02:15:20,070
等等  你们去哪
Wait, where are you going?

1860
02:15:20,350 --> 02:15:22,770
你们不是要送我回家的吗
You were supposed to be my lift home.

1861
02:15:23,040 --> 02:15:24,730
我要怎么离开啊
How will I get out of here?

1862
02:15:25,140 --> 02:15:26,150
天呐
Aw, gee...

1863
02:15:26,150 --> 02:15:29,020
我还有好多故事要讲呢
I've got so many more stories to tell.

1864
02:15:29,020 --> 02:15:30,410
伙计们
Aw, guys.

1865
02:15:30,460 --> 02:15:31,910
天呐
Oh, gee...

